The '''Quadrant Seven''' were a race of [[Humanoid/Legends|humanoids]] from the planet also known as [[Quadrant Seven]]. They were distinguished by a collection of antennae on their heads which resembled [[Human/Legends|Human]] hair. The Quadrant Seven were a peaceful race who, at the time of the [[Clone Wars/Legends|Clone Wars]], had not had a war on their planet for 573 years. They shunned technology and were dedicated to preserving their planet's ecosystems.

